se aufgabenbezogen eine Orientierung für die Prüfungsvorbereitung und das vertiefte Selbststudium.  aThis book contains a compendium of test questions and solutions related to investment and financing. In addition, it includes further exercises for exam preparation and self-study. The 3rd edition has been expanded with new exercises.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 01. Dez 2022) 0aCapital investments. 0aCorporationsxFinance. 0aInvestments. 7aBUSINESS & ECONOMICS / Finance / General.2bisacsh1 aSchneider, Jürgen, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aVorfeld, Michael, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG OWV ebook Paket Lehrbücher Wirtschaftswiss. 2016z9783110491104oZDB-23-OLW08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus DeG Package 2017 Part 1z978311076249508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2017z978311071954308iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2016z9783110485103oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Economics 2016z9783110485158oZDB-23-DBV0 cEPUBz97831104694000 cprintz978311046927140uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311046926440uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110469264423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110469264/original  a978-3-11-071954-3  DG Plus eBook-Package 2017b2017  a978-3-11-076249-5  DG Plus DeG Package 2017 Part 1b2017  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LAEC  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DBVb2016  aZDB-23-DGGb2016  aZDB-23-OLWb2016